<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>New Chat Message</title>
  <style>
    .head-con {
      width: 100%;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    section {
      margin-top: 20px;

    }
    .name{
        color: green;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="head-con">
      <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>
      You have a new message from <span class="name">{{sellername}}</span> regarding <strong>{{itemname}}</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      To view and reply to the message, please click the link below:
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{link}}">Open Chat</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      Please respond as soon as you can to keep the conversation going.
    </p>
    <p>
      Kind regards,<br />
      The Thriftify Team
    </p>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
